data.description: Beautiful single story home, nestled in a lovely location in the westside of El Paso County. This home features great front landscape that will catch the eye.  Entry to a great room and  kitchen and dining, breakfast area, formal dining room, big master bedroom, jacuzzi in master bath. A great private backyard, ready for your family gatherings! Schedule your viewing today!
